CRM Analytics for Complaint Management
Complaint Management Dashboard

The Complaints Management dashboard analyzes customer complaints, providing quick insights into complaint volume, trends, and resolution progress. You can analyze complaints based on channels, subtypes, customers, and representatives.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited Editions where Financial Services Cloud is enabled

You can filter data by products and services types, complaints type, status, financial accounts, duration, and compare with a previous period to analyze progress.
